      "id": "PopularPost2074",
      "post_content": "In the past, [Bad Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bad Moon ) always took a backseat to its counterpart [Crusade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crusade), because black didn't offer the same kinds of creatures white did. In order to make the most of Bad Moon, you need lots of creatures. Generally, the best way to do this is to fill your deck with small, low mana cost black creatures. In Magic, this is called a weenie deck. Back in the days of Revised, black didn't have a lot of efficient creatures to support playing Bad Moon. There was Will o' Wisp and [Black Knight](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Knight), but it wasn't until Fallen Empires gave us [Order of the Ebon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Order of the Ebon) Hand and thrulls that Bad Moon became really useful.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost2074\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">In the past, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bad Moon \" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bad Moon \">Bad Moon </a>always took a backseat to its counterpart <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Crusade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crusade\">Crusade</a>, because black didn't offer the same kinds of creatures white did.  In order to make the most of Bad Moon, you need lots of creatures.  Generally, the best way to do this is to fill your deck with small, low mana cost black creatures.  In Magic, this is called a weenie deck.  Back in the days of Revised, black didn't have a lot of efficient creatures to support playing Bad Moon.  There was Will o' Wisp and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Black Knight\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Knight\">Black Knight</a>, but it wasn't until Fallen Empires gave us <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Order of the Ebon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Order of the Ebon\">Order of the Ebon</a> Hand and thrulls that Bad Moon became really useful.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '2074'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n      